 (Reuters) - Macy's Inc reports same-store sales for July 

 * Same-store sales down 10.7% in July * July same store sales fell 10.7 percent * Sees Q2 earnings per share $0.15 to $0.17 excluding items * July sales fell 10.7 percent to $1.38 billion * Q2 sales fell 9.7 percent to $5.17 billion * July Thomson Reuters Estimates same store sales view was down 9.1 percent * Reuters Estimates Q2 revenue view $5,193.14 million